text: Egg Harbor is a town in Door County in the state of Wisconsin in the United States. The unincorporated area of Carlsville is also within the town. == Geography == The United States Census Bureau says that Egg Harbor has a total area of 119.7 square miles, 69.9% of which is water. == References == == Other websites == * Town of Egg Harbor, Wisconsin website Category:Towns in Wisconsin Category:Door County, Wisconsin
title: Egg Harbor (town), Wisconsin
